weka.dl4j.text.sentenceiterator

Class WekaInstanceSentenceIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.text.sentenceiterator.BaseSentenceIterator
      • weka.dl4j.text.sentenceiterator.WekaInstanceSentenceIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.deeplearning4j.text.sentenceiterator.SentenceIterator

    public class WekaInstanceSentenceIterator
extends org.deeplearning4j.text.sentenceiterator.BaseSentenceIterator
    A Deeplearning4j's sentence iterator for Weka Instances. It considers Strings from a given attribute index. If the String attribute has multiple lines, they are splitted.
